Lissage exponentiel simple pour prÃ©dire Ã  lâhorizon \(h\). \[\hat x_{n,h} = (1-\alpha) \sum_{k=0}^{n-1} \alpha^k x_{n-k}\]

Question 2

ImplÃ©mentation du lissage exponentiel double

h = 1:168
L1 = c()
for(i in 1:n){
  L1 = c(L1, (1-alpha)*sum(kwh[1:i]*alpha^(seq(i-1,0,-1))))
}
L2 = c()
